transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Ha sir boliye.
Customer: Ha sir to sir ye jo aapka d rank aa raha hai Ram Darbar coin isme deal karte hain aap?
Executive: Ha karte hain karte hain.
Customer: To sir isme koi product add kara lijiye na isme koi product add nahi hai aur ye jo product hai na wo d rank me aa raha jab isme koi product add ho jayega na to Google meet pe aap mujhe video call pe batao aisa kya hai mujhe samajh me nahi aa raha hai.
Customer: Ye aap ek hai Ram Darbar coin hmm keyword hai na aap iske lead utha rahe hain consume kar rahe hain matlab lead to koi ek product hai Ram Darbar coin jisme aap deal karte hain.
Executive: Coin hai coin.
Customer: Sorry aap coin hai coin wo aap coin to aap ha to aapke pass wo product hai aap deal karte hain isme.
Executive: Ha karte hain na.
Customer: Achcha achcha to isme aap product add kara lijiye sir.
Executive: Matlab photo ka photo add karu.
Customer: Aap main isme kuch product add nahi hai main ek bar product add karta hu aapko video me bhi bulata hu theek hai aap product karna bata dijiye kis kis naam se aapke product hai iske coin ke theek hai wo photo mujhe de dijiye whatsapp pe aur naam bata dijiye fir main add kar deta hu iske description dal deta hu uske baad aap lead consume kariye koi dikkat nahi hai fir ye aapka a rank me aa jayega abhi d rank me hai.
Customer: Hai na isme koi category add aap mujhe aap mujhe ek kam kijiye aap mujhe whatsapp number bataiye.
Executive: Yahi mera main aapko whatsapp pe hai bhejta hu.
Customer: Bhejo bhejo sir.
Executive: Theek hai sir aur ye jo kal concern humne raise kiya tha wo main close kar de raha hu yahan se kyuki kal baat nahi ho payi thi na aapse puri to ha main aaj office hai to aaj office aa gaye hain to ab system pe to concern jo hai aapka solve ho gaya na sir ye.
Customer: Ha solve ho gaya.
Executive: Okay sir main yahan pe aapko concern wo close kar de raha hu aur baat baki jo aapko catalog inko change karana ho wo bata dijiye aap.
Executive: Feedback le le ye recording aur by the way jo consume kar rahe hain aap Ram Darbar coin isse aapko conversion vagaira mil raha hai na d rank me hum baat kar li aap.
Customer: Customer mil rahe hain lekin abhi filhal me koi confirm nahi hua hai lead mil rahe hain customer koi dikkat nahi hai.
Executive: Aap whatsapp pe hai kijiye main aapko details share karta hu.
Customer: Ek second ek second line par rahiye.
